Package: retailr
Title: Fashion Product Segmentation and Profit-Tier Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vritika", email = "vritika25@iitk.ac.in", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An end-to-end pipeline for segmenting fashion retail products into
    profit tiers (High, Mid, Low) using PCA, t-SNE, cross-validated K-means
    clustering, and kNN classification. Given a raw product dataset the package
    cleans and encodes features, runs the segmentation pipeline, and returns
    actionable upgrade recommendations for each product.
